race.description: Spelling At Coolmore Mt White Handicap (Bm78)
race.comment: VIKTOR (12) big jump in grade out to the 2000m. Covered a stack of ground in the run with a plugging fourth over the 1800m at Randwick Kensington in BM72 grade. Solid each way contender with the right run. WILLIE OPPA (7) chasing his third win from his last four starts and ready for this trip. Will go back from the gate and should get his desired tempo to finish strongly. PLACID PEARL (9) failed to run the 2400m out in the heavy (8) going with a well beaten seventh at this track. Can bounce back on the firmer surface with her strong ratings base. HEAVEN BOUND (3) hitting her straps this prep and worth more than a passing glance. Won over 1900m and goes into the exotics.
